text: ”’Jethabhai Ranabhai Jora”’ (also spelled ”’Jethalal Jora”’) is an Indian politician, Social worker and Vice president of Gujarat Pradesh Congress Committee, former president of Junagadh Congress, former member of Gujarat Legislative Assembly for Junagadh Assembly constituency and Talala Assembly constituency as a member of Indian National Congress. == References == Category:Politicians from Gujarat
title: Jethabhai Jora
